有内涵的时政新媒体。
Connotation of the new political media.
澎湃新闻记者 赵思维 实习生 闫彩琪指令传来，需要清理出舱间的医疗废弃物（后文简称“医废”），保洁员宋彧遇到了进入方舱医院工作以来清运量最大的医废。
Yang Pai journalist Yan-cai Yan-qi, Zhao thinking intern, told her to clean up medical waste from the cabin. Songyu came from the hospital and received the largest amount of medical waste since entering the hospital.
累积的高污染医废堆在出舱间。
Accumulated high-polluting medical waste piles in the compartment.
用夹子不好操作，扫地又增加气溶胶传播的风险，接下来还有清理患者餐余垃圾的任务。
Using a clamp is difficult to operate, and sweeping increases the risk of aerosol transmission, followed by the task of cleaning up patients' food waste.
情急下，宋彧带头抱起医废，装入垃圾袋中。
Songyu or making his name in a garbage bag.
保洁员宋彧倒完垃圾后将空捅摆放在墙角在此过程中，他和队友要用双手撑开袋口，身体还要尽力躬着避开垃圾表面。
His name is Songyu or his family member. His name is Songyu or his name is Yu. His name is Songyu or he comes from the outside.
装满了15个大型垃圾袋后，他们将这些高危垃圾袋封口，一袋袋拎往位于B厅北门约800米处的医废处理工作间。
Filled with 15 large garbage bags, they sealed the bags and carried them to a waste disposal workshop about 800 meters north of Hall B.
口罩和防护服密闭得让人窒息。
Masks and protective clothing are tightly sealed and suffocating.
才拎完第一袋，他就大口喘气，浑身发汗。
When he finished his first bag, he gasped and sweated.
近两小时后，他的耳朵被口罩绳子“割”得生疼、身上被汗湿的地方开始发冷，医废才被清运结束。
Nearly two hours later, his ears were "cut" by a mask rope, his body began to chill where he was sweating, and the scrap was cleared.
保洁员宋彧拉着垃圾桶穿梭在舱内汗流了一波又一波，人极度缺水，穿好的成人尿不湿也没有用上。
Songyu and his garbage can come in waves and sweat in the tank. People are so water scarce that they don't get wet or wet.
过了两个小时，他和队友再次进入出舱间时，他的口罩已经湿透、感染风险增大。
By the time he and his teammates re-entered the cabin two hours later, his mask was soaking wet and at increased risk of infection.
这次出舱后，他感慨：“能够呼吸一口新鲜空气是最幸福的事情。
After leaving the cabin, he lamented: "To be able to breathe fresh air is the happiest thing."
”2月8日，作为东西湖区东山街道办事处工作人员，宋彧主动报名进舱清运医废和患者生活垃圾。
"On February 8, my name is Dongshan Street in the Dongshan Lake. My name is Song Yu.
他所工作的B厅最高峰时约有410余名患者，早、午饭所产生的餐余垃圾几乎装满16个大型垃圾桶和70余个瓦楞纸箱。
He worked in B hall at the peak of about 410 patients, morning and lunch generated waste almost filled with 16 large garbage cans and 70 corrugated box.
“保证舱内一直有多的空桶，确保垃圾及时清运，保障舱内整洁卫生。
"Make sure there are always more empty bins in the hold, ensure the timely removal of garbage, and keep the cabin clean and sanitary.
”这是宋彧他们的工作。
My name is Songyu or their job.
近一个月来，他和同事们每天都循环往复地围着垃圾打转：在舱内装垃圾、运到舱外转运站、把垃圾倒上垃圾车、清洗垃圾桶再摆回原处。
For nearly a month, he and his colleagues have been recycling around the garbage: loading it in, shipping it out to the transfer station, dumping it in the garbage truck, cleaning the garbage can and putting it back in place.
排班没有优化之前，他们每天工作7个多小时，“全身软绵绵”的出舱。
Before scheduling was optimized, they worked more than seven hours a day, "all soft" out of the cabin.
方舱指挥部及时将保洁分工和流程理顺，垃圾桶也增加到50余个，他们工作时长才压缩到3个多小时。
Square cabin command will clean up the division of labor and procedures in a timely manner, garbage cans have increased to more than 50, their working hours compressed into more than three hours.
舱内墙角摆放的垃圾桶“其实，运行方舱医院是摸着石头过河。
The dustbin in the corner of the cabin "In fact, the operation of the cabin hospital is to feel stones across the river.
” 宋彧回忆，一开始，舱内垃圾箱清倒时没有预留的空垃圾箱，只能用塑料袋及瓦楞纸箱暂替。
Songyu or his family name comes from a garbage can that was not reserved when the compartments were emptied or used in plastic bags or corrugated cartons.
消毒喷壶、横向大型拖把、大型黑色塑料袋、消毒设施也是逐步添置。
Disinfection spray pot, large horizontal mop, large black plastic bags, disinfection facilities are also gradually added.
“人生实苦，任何工作都磨人，至少这个工作可以锻炼身体。
"Life is hard, and any job can grind people, at least this job can exercise.
”因为没有预想到工作强度，宋彧没有带足换洗衣服。
My name is Songyu or I don't have enough to change my clothes.
怀孕9个月的妻子放心不下他，打包衣物给他送到住处楼下。
His wife, who was nine months pregnant, worried about him, packed and sent him downstairs.
隔着五米，他妻子把箱子放地上。
Five metres apart, his wife put the box on the ground.
“一定要注意防护，你马上是两个孩子的爸爸了，要有责任。
"You have to be careful. You're going to be the father of two children. You have to be responsible.
”妻子的声音从口罩中闷闷地传来。
"His wife's voice was muffled from the mask.
“这边不用担心，我的防护措施和医护人员是一样的，工作都理顺了，在家把自己照顾好。
"Don't worry about it. I've got the same precautions as the paramedics. The work is straightened out and I'm taking care of myself at home.
”妻子即将面临分娩，他有些自责，那天应该还在工作或者正在隔离，不能陪在妻子身边，看着孩子出生。
His wife was about to give birth, and he blamed himself for being at work or in quarantine that day, unable to stay with his wife and watch the baby go.
